  "text": "For specific inhibition of the A2BAR, PSB1115 (Tocris, Biotrend-Chemikalien) was administered IV via the jugular vein (5 mg/kg/h). This dosing regimen was previously shown to effectively inhibit A2BAR signaling [CITATION_1] . In other experiments, a recently described A2BAR agonist (BAY 60-6583, Bayer HealthCare AG, 60 lg/kg IV via the jugular vein) was used [CITATION_2] .",
